Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 53rd Weekly Dose of Optimism.
What. A. Week. Are aliens real? Are room-temperature superconductors real?=
=20
Whatever the outcome, the excitement is palpable. The timeline is electric.=
=20
Let's get to it.
