ChatGPT. OpenAI&#8217;s more advanced GPT-4 model still outperforms the Lla=
MA2 Chat 70B. For how long, though? Only time will tell.</span></p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;"><span>Tracking the ins-and-outs of LLM performance is not exactly=
 our beat here at </span><em>Not Boring</em><span>. There are hundreds (</s=
pan><em>now thousands?</em><span>) of AI-specific newsletters that have pop=
ped up to do that in recent months. But, it is wild to see the rise of comp=
etition and the speed of progress in such a nascent space. ChatGPT shocked =
the world just 8 months ago, and now there are a plethora of well-resourced=
 and performant alternatives. </span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64)=
; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Open-source foun=
dation models competing with closed ones should be a boon for innovation in=
 the space and a counterbalance against centralized control of the digital =
brains. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-heigh=
t: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong><span>Bonus: </span><a href=3D"https:=
